Symbol.Script_3D:
!! Office Table Round.gsm
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end
if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_resol = 12
pen gs_cont_pen
unID = 1 hotspot A/2,0,0,unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot -A/2,0,0,unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, B/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,-B/2,0,unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot A/2,0,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot -A/2,0,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, B/2,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,-B/2,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1
add -A/2, -B/2, 0
addz ZZYZX call "fa_tabletop_macro" parameters A=A, B=B, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_tabletop_style_m = 9, gs_radius_1 = gs_radius_1, gs_radius_2 = gs_radius_2, gs_tabletop_edge_style_m = gs_tabletop_edge_style_m, gs_table_thickness = gs_table_thickness, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_top_mat = gs_top_mat, gs_top_edge_mat = gs_top_edge_mat, unID = unID, returned_parameters legOffsetLeftX, legOffsetRightX, legOffsetY, unID del 1
call "fa_tableleg_macro" parameters A=A, B=B, ZZYZX = ZZYZX - gs_table_thickness, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_leg_type_m = gs_leg_type_m, gs_leg_width = gs_leg_width, gs_leg_depth = gs_leg_depth, gs_leg_diameter = gs_leg_diameter, gs_leg_frame_width = gs_leg_frame_width, gs_leg_frame_depth = gs_leg_frame_depth, gs_leg_frame_ovhg = gs_leg_frame_ovhg, gs_leg_frame_roller = gs_leg_frame_roller, gs_leg_base_depth = gs_leg_base_depth, gs_leg_base_height = gs_leg_base_height, bLegGroup = 1, legOffsetLeftX = legOffsetLeftX, legOffsetRightX = legOffsetRightX, legOffsetTopY = legOffsetY, legOffsetBottomY = legOffsetY, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_leg_mat = gs_leg_mat, gs_legbase_mat = gs_legbase_mat, unID = unID, returned_parameters unID
del 1
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Office Table Round.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen
if A < 0.2 then A = 0.2 if B < 0.2 then B = 0.2
! Minimal Space call "fa_minimalspace" parameters A=A,B=B, MSFront = MSFront, MSType = 7, unID = 3000
unID = 1 hotspot2 0,0,unID : unID=unID+1
for i=1 to 4 hotspot2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 hotspot2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1
rot2 90 next i del 3
line_type 1
add2 -A/2, -B/2 call "fa_tabletop_macro" parameters A=A, B=B, gs_tabletop_style_m = 9, gs_radius_1 = gs_radius_1, gs_radius_2 = gs_radius_2, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type = gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen = gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen = gs_back_pen, unID = unID del 1
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001
dim gs_leg_type_string[6] gs_leg_type_string[1] = `Прямоугольный` gs_leg_type_string[2] = `Круглая` gs_leg_type_string[3] = `Сплошные` gs_leg_type_string[4] = `Царга` gs_leg_type_string[5] = `T-ножка` gs_leg_type_string[6] = `Двойная T-ножка`
dim gs_tabletop_style_string[9] gs_tabletop_style_string[1] = `Прямоугольный` gs_tabletop_style_string[2] = `Закругленные Углы` gs_tabletop_style_string[3] = `Закругленные Углы с одной Стороны` gs_tabletop_style_string[4] = `Эллипс` gs_tabletop_style_string[5] = `Овал` gs_tabletop_style_string[6] = `Закругленный с Одной Стороны` gs_tabletop_style_string[7] = `Криволинейный Торец` gs_tabletop_style_string[8] = `Криволинейный Торец с Одной Стороны` gs_tabletop_style_string[9] = `Круглая`
dim gs_tabletop_edge_style_string[3] gs_tabletop_edge_style_string[1] = `Прямоугольный` gs_tabletop_edge_style_string[2] = `Закругленный` gs_tabletop_edge_style_string[3] = `Закругленный`
iTabletopStyleMask = 256 ! 9 iLegStyleMask = 127
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "A" range[0.200,] values "B" range[0.200,] values "ZZYZX" range[0.100,]
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then parameters B=A if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then parameters A=B
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then parameters temp_RR=A/2 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "temp_RR" then parameters A=temp_RR*2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then parameters temp_RR=B/2 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "temp_RR" then parameters B=temp_RR*2
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=19
values "gs_resol" range[4,)
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then hideparameter "gs_resol" if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
call "fa_tabletop_macro" parameters A=A, B=B, iTabletopStyleMask = iTabletopStyleMask, gs_tabletop_style = gs_tabletop_style, gs_tabletop_style_m = gs_tabletop_style_m, gs_tabletop_style_string = gs_tabletop_style_string, gs_radius_1 = gs_radius_1, gs_radius_2 = gs_radius_2, gs_tabletop_edge_style = gs_tabletop_edge_style, gs_tabletop_edge_style_m = gs_tabletop_edge_style_m, gs_tabletop_edge_style_string = gs_tabletop_edge_style_string, gs_table_thickness = gs_table_thickness
call "fa_tableleg_macro" parameters A=A, B=B, iLegStyleMask = iLegStyleMask, gs_leg_type = gs_leg_type, gs_leg_type_m = gs_leg_type_m, gs_leg_type_string = gs_leg_type_string
values "gs_ui_current_page" 1
! --- Minimal Space --- values "MSFront" range[0,)
Symbol.Script_UI:
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
pageStartY = 5
iPageIDRoot =-1 iPageIDStyle = 1
! === Page 1 ===================================================================
UI_PAGE iPageIDStyle, iPageIDRoot, `Стиль Столешницы и Ножек`, "uiTab_Style_flat(1)"
dim uiStrings[2] uiStrings[1] = `Стиль Столешницы` uiStrings[2] = `Торец Столешницы`
call "fa_tabletop_macro" parameters A=A, B=B, iTabletopStyleMask = iTabletopStyleMask, gs_tabletop_style_string = gs_tabletop_style_string, gs_tabletop_edge_style_string = gs_tabletop_edge_style_string, uiStrings = uiStrings
ui_separator 138,pageStartY - 5,138,266
dim uiLegStrings[1] uiLegStrings[1] = `Стиль Ножек`
call "fa_tableleg_macro" parameters A=A, B=B, iLegStyleMask = iLegStyleMask, gs_leg_type_string = gs_leg_type_string, uiStrings = uiLegStrings
Symbol.Comment: Стол офисный с стилями ножек и минимальным пространством.
